(740, 740, 1, 'Resonant Touch', 'resonant-touch', 'resonant-touch', '{\"3da30d7e-ecb1-4689-b813-cf5e010cefbc\":{\"titleRaw\":{\"1\":\"My work\"},\"descriptionRaw\":\"\",\"keywords\":[],\"score\":\"\",\"social\":{\"twitter\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]},\"facebook\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]}},\"advanced\":{\"robots\":[],\"canonical\":\"\"}}}', 1, '2025-05-23 11:47:44', '2025-05-23 11:47:44', '7fc0f08e-e822-4430-ac8f-a82200ca9982'),
(741, 741, 1, NULL, '__temp_rdwpgnoshteyuhouyaspadhgmvixaknbgkro', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Resonant Touch\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":true,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Holistic Relational Trauma Integration (and Human Potential)\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> is an intuitive approach to therapy that helps clients realign with their natural inner spaciousness and sense of connection. It is a culmination of my lifelong inquiry into the interplay between mind, body, and relational presence. It is rooted in an embodied awareness of the profound intelligence that guides healing from within.</p><p>The approach centers on creating safe, attuned spaces where healing unfolds organically. Drawing from NARM and BCST, <strong>Resonant Touch</strong> developed as a way to integrate verbal and non-verbal therapeutic approaches. It is grounded in the embodied recognition that we are inherently whole, even in the face of the separation that comes from early adaptations and survival strategies.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> recognizes that the path toward healing requires attunement to the complexities of early life adaptations, addressing both the visible and invisible aspects of human experience. The fundamental assumption we offer is that, on a deeper level of experience, we are always whole and complete. Even within the limitation of our adaptations, there is an underlying health at work. Every survival strategy, no matter how misaligned it may appear, is part of an inherent organizing wisdom.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-05-23 11:47:44', '2025-05-23 11:47:44', 'a607327c-2f99-423c-8329-2bf53f6752c2'),
(742, 742, 1, NULL, '__temp_agnxeknakmcarllnwtarizyftzouuydzlzxx', NULL, '{\"032378b9-225f-4ca4-b509-5bf5b952dde2\":\"My work is not a therapeutic system.\",\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p>My work is not a therapeutic system. It focuses on the essential nature of our beingness as humans, and how we can bring this dimension into our work as therapists. My deeper intention is to encourage therapists into a fundamental trust in the subtle, natural unfolding of life. I am dedicated to supporting individualswhether clients or practitionersin cultivating a stronger connection with themselves and the unseen currents of life force that sustain us all.</p><p>When therapists attune to these underlying structures, they develop a greater capacity to trust these currents of Life Forcesometimes referred to as divine presence or chithat moves through us as an organizing and creative force. Engaging with this force in a direct, non-verbal way, fosters a therapeutic presence that is both spacious and anchored in open-heartedness.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> highlights the interdependent nature of inner spaciousness and resonance, recognizing them as the foundation of any embodied therapy. This basic attunement allows for the exploration of obstacles, adaptations, and survival strategies in a way that encourages natural and effortless disidentification from them.The moment-to-moment, process-oriented nature of this work enables deep psychobiological healing.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-05-23 11:47:44', '2025-05-23 11:47:44', 'd9269c6d-c997-4aa8-8815-dd2d39f6bbd4'),
(743, 743, 1, 'Resonant Touch', 'resonant-touch', 'resonant-touch', '{\"3da30d7e-ecb1-4689-b813-cf5e010cefbc\":{\"titleRaw\":{\"1\":\"My work\"},\"descriptionRaw\":\"\",\"keywords\":[],\"score\":\"\",\"social\":{\"twitter\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]},\"facebook\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]}},\"advanced\":{\"robots\":[],\"canonical\":\"\"}}}', 1, '2025-05-23 11:47:55', '2025-05-23 11:47:55', '5f8a1458-332c-4071-b6a5-d5fa34d140b3'),
(744, 744, 1, NULL, '__temp_agnxeknakmcarllnwtarizyftzouuydzlzxx', NULL, '{\"032378b9-225f-4ca4-b509-5bf5b952dde2\":\"My work is not a therapeutic system.\",\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p><i>My work is not a therapeutic system. </i>It focuses on the essential nature of our beingness as humans, and how we can bring this dimension into our work as therapists. My deeper intention is to encourage therapists into a fundamental trust in the subtle, natural unfolding of life. I am dedicated to supporting individualswhether clients or practitionersin cultivating a stronger connection with themselves and the unseen currents of life force that sustain us all.</p><p>When therapists attune to these underlying structures, they develop a greater capacity to trust these currents of Life Forcesometimes referred to as divine presence or chithat moves through us as an organizing and creative force. Engaging with this force in a direct, non-verbal way, fosters a therapeutic presence that is both spacious and anchored in open-heartedness.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> highlights the interdependent nature of inner spaciousness and resonance, recognizing them as the foundation of any embodied therapy. This basic attunement allows for the exploration of obstacles, adaptations, and survival strategies in a way that encourages natural and effortless disidentification from them.The moment-to-moment, process-oriented nature of this work enables deep psychobiological healing.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-05-23 11:47:55', '2025-05-23 11:47:55', '699c3683-18e5-4b73-8deb-963a366e732c'),
(748, 748, 1, NULL, '__temp_pcjrnvbxjmqtoolywujtybvtyvdkvgnezeqp', NULL, '{\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p><strong>NARM individual sessions</strong> focus on working through patterns of developmental trauma, survival strategies, and identity adaptations, supporting a deeper connection to the authentic self and fostering greater relational and emotional freedom.</p><p><strong>Individual Resonant Touch sessions</strong> bring attention to both developmental dynamics and the deeper currents of life force that sustain and shape the body-mind. Through sensitive presence, therapeutic touch, and relational attunement, we gently engage emotional processes, obstacles to authentic expression, and the release of crystallized patterns held within the system.</p><p>Sessions typically include physical contact, with the client lying fully clothed on a table, allowing the therapist to offer grounded, attuned touch that supports regulation and coherence. This work unfolds within a space of deep listening and embodied awareness, where the natural intelligence of the system is met with respect and curiosity. <strong>Sessions can be held in person in Ljubljana or online, depending on what best supports your process.</strong></p><p>Both formatsongoing individual work and occasional therapy daysoffer a safe, compassionate environment for the organic movement of life energy and the emergence of inner spaciousness and connection.</p>\",\"489bc2dc-2ddb-441d-8ddb-00351993c722\":false}', 1, '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '2025-08-11 12:38:36', 'f6afa982-d296-4b09-a33b-4be642571f4e'),
(749, 749, 1, 'Individual Sessions', 'epr', 'embodied-psychodynamic-resonance', '{\"3da30d7e-ecb1-4689-b813-cf5e010cefbc\":{\"titleRaw\":{\"1\":\"EPR\"},\"descriptionRaw\":\"\",\"keywords\":[],\"score\":\"\",\"social\":{\"twitter\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"How does an EPR Session look like? - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]},\"facebook\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"How does an EPR Session look like? - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]}},\"advanced\":{\"robots\":[],\"canonical\":\"\"}}}', 1, '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '3ae04f2f-89ac-4361-9e7e-ecfac375e0a6'),
(750, 750, 1, NULL, '__temp_znuenhitigyhlkyqycfzpwqpxqvzkywxfzci', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Individual Sessions\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"right\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":true,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Individual sessions include both, NARM-based sessions and Resonant Touch sessions.\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p>In my practice, I offer individual NARM and Resonant Touch sessions, as well as various teaching and learning formats. My work is rooted in the&nbsp;<strong>NeuroAffective Relational Model (NARM)</strong> and in the&nbsp;<strong>biodynamic approach to Craniosacral Therapy</strong>, and is also informed by other&nbsp;<strong>body-oriented</strong> and&nbsp;<strong>trauma-based therapeutic modalities</strong>. Additionally, I have developed&nbsp;<strong>Resonant Touch</strong>, a synthesis of these influences with my own experiential understanding of relational healing.</p><p><strong>Individual sessions</strong> include both, NARM-based sessions and Resonant Touch sessions.</p><p><strong>NARM individual sessions</strong> focus on working through patterns of developmental trauma, survival strategies, and identity adaptations, supporting a deeper connection to the authentic self and fostering greater relational and emotional freedom.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '17612466-e365-4bff-bdfe-26c76b261c7f'),
(751, 751, 1, NULL, '__temp_pcjrnvbxjmqtoolywujtybvtyvdkvgnezeqp', NULL, '{\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p><strong>Individual Resonant Touch sessions</strong> bring attention to both developmental dynamics and the deeper currents of life force that sustain and shape the body-mind. Through sensitive presence, therapeutic touch, and relational attunement, we gently engage emotional processes, obstacles to authentic expression, and the release of crystallized patterns held within the system. Sessions typically include physical contact, with the client lying fully clothed on a table, allowing the therapist to offer grounded, attuned touch that supports regulation and coherence. This work unfolds within a space of deep listening and embodied awareness, where the natural intelligence of the system is met with respect and curiosity. Both formats offer a safe, compassionate environment for the organic movement of life energy and the emergence of inner spaciousness and connection.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '2025-05-26 12:42:29', '0a22cef8-6d4e-46bf-bdc2-31e2f4edbe87'),
