(773, 773, 1, NULL, '__temp_wwpocgdqesdfaitiqdaitzxlizthoegcmwtj', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Supervision & Trainings\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":false,\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p><strong>Individual supervisions</strong> support practitioners in their professional development from a relational perspective. NARM individual supervisions focus on the application of NARM principles in therapeutic work, exploring survival patterns, relational dynamics, emotional processing, and the therapists own embodied presence within the clinical setting. Resonant Touch individual supervisions are available for those who have trained in Resonant Touch with me, offering a space to deepen sensitivity to the life force, relational attunement, and awareness of how developmental and survival patterns are held within the body-mind.</p><p><strong>Group supervisions</strong> are self-organized and provide a reflective space to explore therapeutic work in a supportive environment. We address the application of NARM principles in clinical practice, the navigation of countertransference dynamics, working through moments of stuckness, and developing comfort with the unknown. Participants bring case material, clinical questions, and personal reflections, fostering an environment for learning and mutual growth. Group supervisions can also be organized around specific themes related to NARM, offering more specific deep-dive explorations.</p><p><strong>Active coaching</strong> groups offer a guided, experiential environment where participants actively practice applying NARM principles. These groups provide a space for participants to explore their own authentic therapeutic impulses, integrate principles into their personal styles of working, and deepen their embodied understanding of relational healing. The focus is on supporting authentic learning rather than rigid application, with an emphasis on safety, creativity, and natural unfolding.</p>\",\"fc438791-5351-42a6-8fe8-98bf5b31a0d8\":[{\"col1\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col3\":\"primary\"}]}', 1, '2025-05-26 12:55:46', '2025-05-26 13:17:25', 'b73366ae-9ec3-42ee-9e42-5a164b27bab4'),
