(937, 937, 1, NULL, '__temp_jgxgughuwafokgwtclsjuzocoqfftoiubwih', NULL, '{\"49e3e828-6795-49c5-a82b-3360a0b3664d\":\"Exploring the Heart of NARM Through Immersive Practice. \\n\\nNARM Deepening Days are a dedicated space for those who wish to engage more fully with the principles of the NeuroAffective Relational Model (NARM). These days are designed for practitioners, students, and individuals already familiar with NARM who are looking to deepen their embodied understanding of this powerful model for healing developmental and relational trauma.\",\"eca88837-37fe-4366-9c04-3b186a4046b3\":\"<p>NARM Deepening Days are a dedicated space for those who wish to engage more fully with the principles of the NeuroAffective Relational Model (NARM). These days are designed for practitioners, students, and individuals already familiar with NARM who are looking to deepen their embodied understanding of this powerful model for healing developmental and relational trauma.</p><p>Each Deepening Day will focus on a specific theme central to the NARM approach.&nbsp;</p><p>These gatherings are <i>experiential and practice-oriented</i>, combining short teaching segments with reflective exercises, active coaching, and live demo sessions. The intention is to create a safe and focused environment for deepening insight, refining relational skills, and exploring how NARMs principles come alive in the moment-to-moment therapeutic process.</p><ul><li>Life Force beyond Adaptations (online)</li><li>Holding Without Fixing: The Role of Touch in a NARM-Oriented Process (at the venue)</li><li>The Gift of Countertransference Dynamics (online)</li></ul>\",\"6cbe1a93-eb4b-48f0-b47c-fc314d657898\":false}', 1, '2025-05-26 13:30:49', '2025-05-26 13:30:49', 'eb3a71d8-3b57-4329-bd8b-05f0b7c8a308'),
