(1004, 1004, 1, NULL, '__temp_ixpbcoywdhyqxpvrgaubccgfdjffnixxvnac', NULL, '{\"fc6a7918-0089-4f87-b9a9-929c37825f1f\":\"It is important to understand that these adaptive behaviors are not to be judged. They served an essential role in helping individuals survive past relational wounds. This is precisely why the term adaptive self is often preferred over false selfto honor the intelligence and necessity of these responses. Still, while these strategies were once protective, they can become obstacles when seeking genuine, mutual, and enduring connection.\",\"77c6a620-da05-48cc-9749-6236ddb2d19a\":\"Karima Valentina Hoevar\"}', 1, '2025-05-27 09:34:38', '2025-05-27 09:34:38', '48ed1902-2b48-4143-87e3-811689dba7ec'),
