(1019, 1019, 1, NULL, '__temp_ivgtrvwnhslqrskkuotlijerlitrswcubryb', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Resonant Touch\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"right\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":false,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Holistic Relational Trauma Integration (and Human Potential)My work is not a therapeutic system.\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> is an intuitive approach to therapy that helps clients realign with their natural inner spaciousness and sense of connection. It is a culmination of my lifelong inquiry into the interplay between mind, body, and relational presence. It is rooted in an embodied awareness of the profound intelligence that guides healing from within.</p><p>The approach centers on creating safe, attuned spaces where healing unfolds organically. Drawing from NARM and BCST, <strong>Resonant Touch</strong> developed as a way to integrate verbal and non-verbal therapeutic approaches. It is grounded in the embodied recognition that we are inherently whole, even in the face of the separation that comes from early adaptations and survival strategies.</p><h2><strong>My work is not a therapeutic system.</strong></h2><p><i>My work is not a therapeutic system. </i>It focuses on the essential nature of our beingness as humans, and how we can bring this dimension into our work as therapists. My deeper intention is to encourage therapists into a fundamental trust in the subtle, natural unfolding of life. I am dedicated to supporting individualswhether clients or practitionersin cultivating a stronger connection with themselves and the unseen currents of life force that sustain us all.</p><p>When therapists attune to these underlying structures, they develop a greater capacity to trust these currents of Life Forcesometimes referred to as divine presence or chithat moves through us as an organizing and creative force. Engaging with this force in a direct, non-verbal way, fosters a therapeutic presence that is both spacious and anchored in open-heartedness.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> highlights the interdependent nature of inner spaciousness and resonance, recognizing them as the foundation of any embodied therapy. This basic attunement allows for the exploration of obstacles, adaptations, and survival strategies in a way that encourages natural and effortless disidentification from them.The moment-to-moment, process-oriented nature of this work enables deep psychobiological healing.</p>\",\"fc438791-5351-42a6-8fe8-98bf5b31a0d8\":[{\"col1\":\"/resonant-touch\",\"col2\":\"Read more\",\"col3\":\"normalLink\"}]}', 1, '2025-05-27 09:39:24', '2025-05-27 09:39:24', 'ca49ac6d-b345-4f4e-8911-fafd1d2288a9'),
