(1131, 1131, 1, 'About Me', 'about-me', 'about-me', '{\"3da30d7e-ecb1-4689-b813-cf5e010cefbc\":{\"titleRaw\":{\"1\":\"About me\"},\"descriptionRaw\":\"\",\"keywords\":[],\"score\":\"\",\"social\":{\"twitter\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"About Me - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]},\"facebook\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"About Me - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]}},\"advanced\":{\"robots\":[],\"canonical\":\"\"}}}', 1, '2025-08-11 09:55:26', '2025-08-11 09:55:26', '7fb43783-6e01-4297-a317-d8d960cebf95'),
(1132, 1132, 1, NULL, '__temp_lekvchmjekxlrsvnukjweeivpobcycywklae', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"About me\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":true,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Karima Valentina Hoevar\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p>From an early age, I have been deeply attuned to human relationshipsthe ways we connect, misunderstand, and heal. My sensitivity to the spaces between people, shaped by early experiences, led me on a journey of self-inquiry, acceptance, and mindfulness. This path evolved into a professional commitment to trauma-informed therapeutic approaches. I have spent years studying and integrating various therapeutic modalities, always with an emphasis on cultivating presence, inner spaciousness, and relational attunement.</p><p>Since 2011, I have been teaching and co-teaching seminars on Biodynamic Craniosacral Therapy (BCST) in Slovenia and internationally. My work with BCST has provided insights into the bodys inherent wisdom and capacity for self-regulation. Since 2015, I have been part of the teaching team and a supervisor for NeuroAffective Relational Model (NARM) trainings across Europe. I am currently participating in Time Wisdom Training (TWT), facilitated by Thomas Hbl.</p><p>Throughout the years of practice, I am in the process of developing a process-oriented therapeutic approach called <strong>Resonant Touch</strong>, which integrates my understanding of wholeness with principles from NARM and BCST.</p><p>I currently live and work in Ljubljana, Slovenia, where I hold my private practice. While Ljubljana is my main base, I regularly travel due to my teaching and therapeutic work. I occasionally offer sessions in Germanyprimarily in Berlinwhen invited, creating opportunities for in-person connection beyond my home practice.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-08-11 09:55:26', '2025-08-11 09:55:26', '27713d29-6166-4adc-9035-38358f840533'),
