(1217, 1217, 1, NULL, '__temp_rdwpgnoshteyuhouyaspadhgmvixaknbgkro', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Resonant Touch\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":true,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Holistic Relational Trauma Integration\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<h2>Resonant Touch Learning Spaces, SV, Group-SV, Active Coaching, NARM Deepening Days</h2>\"}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:16:28', '2025-08-11 10:16:28', '6ce9c27f-88ab-4eaf-af5c-232a7ebc44f4'),
(1218, 1218, 1, 'Resonant Touch', 'resonant-touch', 'resonant-touch', '{\"3da30d7e-ecb1-4689-b813-cf5e010cefbc\":{\"titleRaw\":{\"1\":\"My work\"},\"descriptionRaw\":\"\",\"keywords\":[],\"score\":\"\",\"social\":{\"twitter\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]},\"facebook\":{\"handle\":null,\"title\":\"Resonant Touch - Karima Hoevar\",\"imageId\":\"\",\"description\":[]}},\"advanced\":{\"robots\":[],\"canonical\":\"\"}}}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:16:57', '2025-08-11 10:16:57', '4ec64f69-ba0d-4014-a6fd-84582da20c34'),
(1219, 1219, 1, NULL, '__temp_rdwpgnoshteyuhouyaspadhgmvixaknbgkro', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Resonant Touch\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":true,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Holistic Relational Trauma Integration\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> is an intuitive relational approach to therapy that helps clients realign with their natural inner spaciousness and sense of connection. It is a culmination of my lifelong inquiry into the interplay between mind, body, and relational presence. It is rooted in an embodied awareness of the profound intelligence that guides healing from within.</p><p>The approach centers on creating safe, attuned spaces where healing unfolds organically. Drawing from NARM and BCST, <strong>Resonant Touch</strong> developed as a way to integrate verbal and non-verbal therapeutic approaches. It is grounded in the embodied recognition that we are inherently whole, even in the face of the separation that comes from early adaptations and survival strategies.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> recognizes that the path toward healing requires attunement to the complexities of early life adaptations, addressing both the visible and invisible aspects of human experience. The fundamental assumption we offer is that, on a deeper level of experience, we are always whole and complete. Even within the limitation of our adaptations, there is an underlying health at work. Every survival strategy, no matter how misaligned it may appear, is part of an inherent organizing wisdom.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:16:57', '2025-08-11 10:16:57', '8f6449dd-8fb8-42ce-8850-44ac73abb8f2'),
(1220, 1220, 1, NULL, '__temp_aybtmzrkapmevafpbszdnqxzgdrdqmcangwh', NULL, '{\"08a88bb4-156c-4633-84f5-5cd9f5b24e0e\":[\"46\"]}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:16:58', '2025-08-11 10:16:58', 'be7da5ec-d4af-445f-bd95-7c759eb34a6a'),
(1221, 1221, 1, NULL, '__temp_agnxeknakmcarllnwtarizyftzouuydzlzxx', NULL, '{\"032378b9-225f-4ca4-b509-5bf5b952dde2\":\"My work is not a therapeutic system.\",\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p>Rather than offering a fixed system, Resonant Touch emerges as a relational frame of practice, grounded in presence, somatic attunement, and trust in the intelligence of the system. It focuses on the essential nature of our beingness as humans, and how we can bring this dimension into our work as therapists. My deeper intention is to encourage therapists into a fundamental trust in the subtle, natural unfolding of life. I am dedicated to supporting individualswhether clients or practitionersin cultivating a stronger connection with themselves and the unseen currents of life force that sustain us all.</p><p>When therapists attune to these underlying structures, they develop a greater capacity to trust these currents of Life Forcesometimes referred to as divine presence or chithat moves through us as an organizing and creative force. Engaging with this force in a direct, non-verbal way, fosters a therapeutic presence that is both spacious and anchored in open-heartedness.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch</strong> highlights the interdependent nature of inner spaciousness and resonance, recognizing them as the foundation of any embodied therapy. This basic attunement allows for the exploration of obstacles, adaptations, and survival strategies in a way that encourages natural and effortless disidentification from them.The moment-to-moment, process-oriented nature of this work enables deep psychobiological healing.</p>\",\"489bc2dc-2ddb-441d-8ddb-00351993c722\":false}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:16:58', '2025-08-11 10:16:58', 'a5c0fd21-a31e-47b1-baf3-e1bbe70c5a2e'),
