(1263, 1263, 1, NULL, '__temp_wjenxdytewgpkoxotzfmwvcsmgqiilfwmfjz', NULL, '{\"032378b9-225f-4ca4-b509-5bf5b952dde2\":\"Resonant Touch Learning Spaces, SV, Group-SV, Actice Coaching, NARM Deepening Days\",\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p><strong>Resonant Touch Learning Spaces</strong></p><p>Emerging from years of embodied therapeutic work, including NARM and Biodynamic Craniosacral Therapy, these learning spaces invite presence, curiosity, and experiential exploration. Rather than offering a fixed method, Resonant Touch opens a field of relational depth where healing unfolds through subtle awareness, resonance, and trust in the natural intelligence of the moment.</p><p>The learning currently unfolds in two formats:&nbsp;<strong>Resonant Touch Immersions</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Resonant Touch Circles</strong>. These spaces support embodied integration, shared inquiry, and intuitive attunement.</p><p>New Resonant Touch Circles may be offered in the future, creating further opportunities for ongoing exploration. For now, these two formats hold the current expression of Resonant Touch learning.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch Immersions</strong>&nbsp;are three-day experiential gatherings that introduce participants to the foundational principles of Resonant Touch. These immersions are relational and body-basednot focused on technique, but on sensing, presence, and intuitive engagement. Grounded in a biodynamic orientation to life force and the developmental insights of NARM, the work unfolds through attunement, shared reflection, and embodied inquiry.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch Circles</strong>&nbsp;are longer-term group spaces, held over time, where a deeper exploration of the work takes place. The first of these began in 2022 and continues as a living field of ongoing inquiry and co-creation. These spaces are not trainings, but relational containers in which the approach itself continues to evolve and take shape through shared experience and trust in the unknown.</p>\",\"489bc2dc-2ddb-441d-8ddb-00351993c722\":false}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:25:49', '2025-08-11 10:25:49', '0fa00886-c81c-4d54-a1c5-e9b6a59c8da3'),
