(1309, 1309, 1, NULL, '__temp_wjenxdytewgpkoxotzfmwvcsmgqiilfwmfjz', NULL, '{\"66af9589-1520-49a8-982e-6ddca319d308\":\"<p><strong>Resonant Touch Immersions</strong>&nbsp;are three-day experiential gatherings that introduce participants to the foundational principles of Resonant Touch. These immersions are relational and body-basednot focused on technique, but on sensing, presence, and intuitive engagement. Grounded in a biodynamic orientation to life force and the developmental insights of NARM, the work unfolds through attunement, shared reflection, and embodied inquiry.</p><p><strong>Resonant Touch Circles</strong>&nbsp;are longer-term group spaces, held over time, where a deeper exploration of the work takes place. The first of these began in 2022 and continues as a living field of ongoing inquiry and co-creation. These spaces are not trainings, but relational containers in which the approach itself continues to evolve and take shape through shared experience and trust in the unknown.</p>\",\"489bc2dc-2ddb-441d-8ddb-00351993c722\":false}', 1, '2025-08-11 10:51:34', '2025-08-11 10:51:34', '8713e891-a7a6-4304-89f0-ab6de2766eed'),
