(1394, 1394, 1, NULL, '__temp_hhyhsiuekblncnkupgdjswstvzhnkyodvgno', NULL, '{\"eca88837-37fe-4366-9c04-3b186a4046b3\":\"<p>The Resonant Touch Circle is an ongoing small group of experienced practitioners engaged in long-term embodied exploration. Together, we meet regularly in a field of presence, resonance, and intuitive learning.</p><p>This group began in 2022 as a co-creative process without a formal structure, and over time, it became the ground from which the core principles of the Resonant Touch approach emerged. It remains a vital space of shared inquiry and mutual deepening.</p><p>This circle is not open to new members, but continues to evolve as a living, relational practice space.</p>\",\"49e3e828-6795-49c5-a82b-3360a0b3664d\":\"Ongoing Relational Field of Practice\",\"6cbe1a93-eb4b-48f0-b47c-fc314d657898\":false}', 1, '2025-08-11 11:12:19', '2025-08-11 11:12:33', 'b2fbbc62-9f93-4d6d-bc99-65a102d76c19'),
