(1507, 1507, 1, NULL, '__temp_udqoqcepiwpzvzikxwpoimphvwmgwupcaeqp', NULL, '{\"61d1d186-dff7-4cbd-b901-256e496e4472\":\"Learning spaces\",\"5b3cf7ba-6a30-467b-8e4d-220f4e2b9105\":\"left\",\"329bb1a1-e734-46d1-8cb5-c3d843e6e98a\":false,\"e5c63454-6cc2-464a-857b-f5eb1ee3d2b2\":\"Resonant Touch Learning Spaces\",\"5f2d23e1-9a53-4f0f-8982-2bbfc0814ee8\":\"<p>Emerging from years of embodied therapeutic work, including NARM and Biodynamic Craniosacral Therapy, these learning spaces invite presence, curiosity, and experiential exploration. Rather than offering a fixed method, Resonant Touch opens a field of relational depth where healing unfolds through subtle awareness, resonance, and trust in the natural intelligence of the moment.</p><p>The learning currently unfolds in two formats:&nbsp;<strong>Resonant Touch Immersions</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Resonant Touch Circles</strong>. These spaces support embodied integration, shared inquiry, and intuitive attunement.</p><p>New Resonant Touch Circles may be offered in the future, creating further opportunities for ongoing exploration. For now, these two formats hold the current expression of Resonant Touch learning.</p>\"}', 1, '2025-08-11 12:23:14', '2025-08-11 12:23:14', 'ee3eb0fc-eb2b-46e2-b3fe-9b8e51be67d9'),
